title: The West Country at Westminster
text:
Credit: ITV News Ian Axton sits down with Bristol North West Conservative MP Charlotte Leslie, Labour's Luke Pollard and former Conservative MP Mark Reckless, now UKIP's economic spokesman.
They debate the important issues of the day, including poverty, the Labour leadership and Europe.
